(2148, 235, 'main-first-p', 'The answer to a question we are asked almost every day: Does programmatic replace humans?'),
(2149, 235, '_main-first-p', 'field_54172dc9d0281'),
(2150, 235, 'main-p', 'Technology is being used to replace some of the menial tasks, but people are required to optimize campaigns, and to plan strategies, and well, do the strategic thinking.\r\n \r\nAutomation does not mean technology is a substitute for a quality customer experience. At Gamut, we employ Smart Service to make our technology work hardest for you.\r\nGamuts Programmatic solution differentiates itself by going the extra mile: high quality inventory and partners, try-it-before-you-buy-it testing, and proprietary focused yield optimization.\r\n\r\nGamuts Programmatic solution differentiates itself in the extras: private exchanges, try-before-you-buy-it testing, and yield optimization. Our technology optimizes across the inventory value spectrum  across display, video, and mobile  so each party can be confident that their dollars are'),
